13#include "absl/types/optional.h"
14#include "api/units/data_rate.h"
15
16namespace webrtc {
17class LinkCapacityEstimator {
18 public:
19 LinkCapacityEstimator();
20 DataRate UpperBound() const;
21 DataRate LowerBound() const;
22 void Reset();
23 void OnOveruseDetected(DataRate acknowledged_rate);
24 void OnProbeRate(DataRate probe_rate);
25 bool has_estimate() const;
26 DataRate estimate() const;
27
28 private:
29 friend class GoogCcStatePrinter;
30 void Update(DataRate capacity_sample, double alpha);
31
32 double deviation_estimate_kbps() const;
33 absl::optional<double> estimate_kbps_;
34 double deviation_kbps_ = 0.4;
35};
36} // namespace webrtc
